definition: Roh Tae-woo (1932-), South Korean politician, president 1988-1993
(old) rice vessel/black/old variant of 廬|庐[lu2]/(slang) (Tw) troublesome/fussy
surname Lu/abbr. for Luxembourg 盧森堡|卢森堡[Lu2 sen1 bao3]
Mt Tai 泰山[Tai4 Shan1] in Shandong/abbr. for Thailand
to be stupid/to cheat or deceive/me or I (modest)

sentences.english: Since Roh Tae Woocame to power, never for a moment demands for his resignation ceased.
sentences.chinese: 盧泰愚執政以來，要求他下臺的呼聲從未間斷過。
